Dynamic Angular Application.
    - if View Interacts with the Controller For Dynamic data then such type of Angular Application called as
    Dynamic Angular Application.

Steps to Create the Dynamic Angular Application.

Step 1.
    Download the Angular Framework by using bower.


1.bower.json

{
    "name":"nareshit",
    "dependencies":{
        "angular":"~1.6.0"
    }

}


2. .bowerrc.json
-
{
    "directory":"bower_components"
}


> bower install

"bower_components / angular / angular.min.js"



Step 2.

    Declare the ng-app directive with the logical  name of web application.


Step 3.

    Declare the Controller by using "ng-controller" directive


Step 4.

    Instantiate the Module ( Getting the Entire Web Page Controll).


Step 5.

    Implement the Controller.

    app.controller("ctrl" , function($scope){

        $scope.var_one = "Hello";

    });



